<img width="768" height="1024" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A-Fendi-bag.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image lazyload" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A-Fendi-bag.jpg 768w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A-Fendi-bag-449x598.jpg 449w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A-Fendi-bag-180x240.jpg 180w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A-Fendi-bag-360x480.jpg 360w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A-Fendi-bag-450x600.jpg 450w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /> An outfit is incomplete without two things: confidence and a bag. No matter how fabulous and expensive a dress looks on you, if it isn’t paired with a bag, your appearance won’t have that “Bam, look at me, I’m a fashionista” effect. Bags are faithful companions to clothes, complementing them and highlighting their beauty. One unique thing about a bag is its versatility, possessing the ability to suit any occasion. Similar to accessories like earrings and neck chains, bags communicate a lot about an individual’s personality. There is an unpopular saying that goes, “A bag speaks louder than words”. Owning a bag that reflects your personality is important because it allows you to accurately define your style. Here are five different bag suggestions to add to your wardrobe. Handbags are pictured through a window of a Coach store in Pasadena, California (photo Reuters) This is a common bag type that exists in the wardrobes of many women across the world. When it comes to listing essential bags every lady should own, a handbag is a staple. Sometimes, it is hard to imagine a lady walking down the streets without a fabulous medium-sized leather handbag.
Handbags are like the crème de la crème of the bag industry, particularly the leather ones that scream expensive. So, if you are looking for a bag to reflect the chic and sophistication in your personality, this is an ideal choice. Backpack A tourist with her backpack | Image: Fred Perrotta Quite a number of us wore this while growing up. Backpacks are not only fun. To a certain extent, comfortable and functional as well. With fashion-forward innovations, they appear in various shapes and sizes and are a suitable choice for the working-class lady who doesn’t want to carry a briefcase but still wants to appear modern, professional, and classy. Totes bags <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1671659 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-598x598.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1280" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-598x598.jpg 598w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-58x58.jpg 58w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-116x116.jpg 116w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-100x100.jpg 100w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-200x200.jpg 200w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-240x240.jpg 240w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-480x480.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik-600x600.jpg 600w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Tote-Ethnik.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Environmentally friendly products are becoming a trend in the world, and what better way to tap into this trend than tote bags? Often used as shopping bags, tote bags help reduce the number of plastic bags used while giving you a stylish appearance. Durability and versatility are two major features of the tote bag. And the best part about this trend is the multiple variations it comes in. Tote bags can be made from plain fabric, patterns, or prints.
Want to save the world from climate change? Time to pick up your phone and call that friend’s sister’s boyfriend’s friend who sells totes bags. Wristlet <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1671664 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Victoria-beckhams-wristlet-bag-523x598.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1463" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Victoria-beckhams-wristlet-bag-523x598.jpg 523w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Victoria-beckhams-wristlet-bag-210x240.jpg 210w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Victoria-beckhams-wristlet-bag-420x480.jpg 420w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Victoria-beckhams-wristlet-bag-525x600.jpg 525w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Victoria-beckhams-wristlet-bag.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Move over handbags, the wristlet is in town. There is something about this bag that makes you want to stare deeply at it and say confidently to yourself, “I have to own that.” The wristlet, as its name suggests, is worn on the wrist and is very fashionable. Putting a twisted spin on the definition of a bag, the wristlet gives your outfit a dramatic flair and unlocks your potential to become a trendsetter. If you still have doubts about getting this bag, we have five words for you: Coach outlet Fall ’20 fashion show. Bucket bag <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1671662 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag-449x598.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1707" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag-449x598.jpg 449w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag-864x1152.jpg 864w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag-180x240.jpg 180w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag-360x480.jpg 360w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag-450x600.jpg 450w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Charles-and-Keith-Bucket-Bag.jpg 1152w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Yes, there is a bag called a “bucket bag.” With a beautiful strap and a sleek style, this bag proves to rise to the occasion when paired with an outfit. It’s the type of bag that commands attention and comprises mouth-watering and jaw-dropping details like pearls, stones, and brooches.
Break free from the norm and explore a bag that is cute, not too out there, and reveals a quirky side of you. THE BAGGY TIP One piece of advice: when deciding on a bag, pay close attention to the fabric, size, and, most importantly, the details. We cannot stress this enough: details are everything.
Time to bag up! I hope you enjoyed reading this article as much as I did writing it. Remember to share it with someone you know.